title: 🔴 LIVE! Phineas and Ferb Season 1 Full Episodes! | @disneychannelanimation
description:
Ferb! I know what we're gonna do today! Watch the full first season of Phineas and Ferb! 

Season 1 Episode 1 Rollercoaster / Candace Loses Her Head
Phineas and Ferb build the coolest rollercoaster ever in their backyard! On Candace's birthday, the family takes a trip to Mount Rushmore.

Season 1 Episode 2 The Fast and the Phineas / Lawn Gnome Beach Party of Terror!
The boys convert Mom's car into a giant remote-controlled car and enter it in a race! The boys decide to make a tropical beach paradise in their very own backyard.

Season 1 Episode 3 The Magnificent Few / S'winter
Phineas and Ferb become real cowboys as they wrangle a stampede of cattle through Danville's city streets. It's wintertime in the summertime!

Season 1 Episode 4 Are You My Mummy? / Flop Starz
Phineas and Ferb search for a mummy to call their own. Phineas and Ferb conspire to become one hit wonders.

Season 1 Episode 5 Raging Bully / Lights, Candace, Action!
Phineas is challenged by Buford, the local bully, to an all out thumb war. Candace's dreams of glamour turn into monstrous nightmares.

Season 1 Episode 6 Get That Bigfoot Outa My Face! / Tree To Get Ready
Phineas and Ferb organize a full day of summer camp activities! Phineas and Ferb decide to build the ultimate tree house.

Season 1 Episode 7 It's About Time! 
Phineas and Ferb find a time machine!

Season 1 Episode 8 Jerk De Soleil / Toy to the World
Phineas and Ferb get everyone together and put on their own circus! The boys invent a toy that becomes the most popular toy in the world.

Season 1 Episode 9 One Good Scare Ought To Do It!
Isabella is inflicted with an extreme case of hiccups!

Season 1 Episode 10 Hard Day's Knight, A / I, Brobot
Candace gets stuck in a suit of armor and is mistaken for the Black Knight. The boys create an army of robots to get all their projects done.

Season 1 Episode 11 Mom's Birthday Episode / Journey to the Center of Candace
Phineas and Ferb go out of their way to give mom the best birthday ever. The boys build a shrinking submarine and end up in Candace's stomach!

Season 1 Episode 12 Run Away Runway / I Scream, You Scream
Phineas and Ferb create a clothing line that completely personifies summer. The boys make Isabella the world's biggest ice cream sundae.

Season 1 Episode 13 It's a Mud, Mud, Mud, Mud World / The Ballad of Badbeard
The boys create a super safe car for Candace so she can learn to drive. The kids set out on an open seas adventure.

Season 1 Episode 14 Dude, We're Getting the Band Back Together 
Phineas and Ferb put a big stadium concert together for Dad.

Season 1 Episode 15 Ready for the Bettys / The Flying Fishmonger
Phineas and Ferb accidentally stumble upon Agent P's secret lair! The boys help their grandfather relive his glory days as a daredevil.

Season 1 Episode 16 Phineas and Ferb Get Busted
The boys get shipped off to military school.

Season 1 Episode 17 Greece Lightning / Leave the Busting to Us!
The boys recreate a chariot race after learning about ancient Greece at the museum. For once Candace has someone on her side - a reality show to help her bust her brothers.

Season 1 Episode 18 Crack That Whip / The Best Lazy Day Ever
Phineas and Ferb set up a roller derby rink so Grandma Betty Jo can skate against her arch rival! It's such a nice day that Phineas and Ferb have decided to do nothing.

Season 1 Episode 19 Boyfriend From 27,000 B.C. / Voyage to the Bottom of Buford
Phineas and Ferb discover a caveman who falls for Candace! After Buford loses his goldfish, Phineas and Ferb help him search for it.

Season 1 Episode 20 Put that Putter Away / Does This Duckbill Make Me Look Fat?
While Candace is sick in bed, she asks Stacy to cover for her and monitor Phineas and Ferb. When the boys invent a body transporter, it actually works...on Candace and Perry.

Season 1 Episode 21 Traffic Cam Caper / Bowl-R-Rama Drama
Dad gets caught speeding from a traffic cam at the intersection down the street. Phineas and Ferb decide to break a world record by building the largest bowling ball ever!

Season 1 Episode 22 The Monster of Phineas-n-Ferbenstein / Oil on Candace
The Grandparents tell the boys about Ferb's ancestor, Victor von Phineastein and Ferbgor! The family goes to an art exhibit where Django's dad is exhibiting his art a la Christo.

Season 1 Episode 23 Unfair Science Fair / Unfair Science Fair Redux
The boys help Baljeet put together his summer school science fair project!

Season 1 Episode 24 Out to Launch
The boys decide to build a rocket ship and travel up in space.

Season 1 Episode 25 Got Game? / Comet Kermilian
When Buford claims that ""boys are better at sports,"" Isabella challenges him to a contest! Jeremy invites Candace to the park.

Season 1 Episode 26 Out of Toon / Hail Doofania!
The boys make a cartoon. Doof's brother gets elected.

Available on Disney Channel and Disney+

title: PJ Masks Full Episodes | PJ Seeker | 1 Hour | Cartoons for Kids | Animation for Kids
description:
Brand NEW Episodes only on Disney Junior
►Subscribe for more PJ Masks videos: http://bit.ly/2gsj5gv
 
PJ Masks Power Heroes - Power heroes Catboy, Owlette and Gekko are joined by new heroes, creating a bigger, even better team. Good thing, too, as new villains are in town. Our heroes will take them on in the city, space, and the frozen wilderness of Iceworld. As Catboy says, “if badness is everywhere, we’ll be everywhere.” 
 
PJ Masks - By day 6 year olds Connor, Amaya and Greg go to school like everyone else. But when something goes awry in the city, these special kids, filled with curiosity and a sense of justice get ready for their mission – but they have to wait until night fall when the city is asleep and they can go un detected. Instead of going to bed like all the other children, when our heroes get their pyjamas on, they magically transform into super heroes and become the PJ Masks. Here come Catboy – super fast and agile, Gekko – super strong and can scale walls and Owlette – with the ability to fly and see great distances. Together these three can tackle any situation – PJ Masks they’re on their way into the night to save the day!
 
Meet The Characters: 
 
Catboy - Incredibly fast! Amazingly agile! Able to hear the quietest sounds across unbelievable distances. When adventure beckons, the amazing Catboy leaps to the rescue!
 
Owlette - She can fly! Has super eyesight! And when she flaps her powerful wings, the baddies are sent flying… Keep your “Owl Eyes!” on Owlette!
 
Gekko - He’s strong, sticky and a master of camouflage! He’s ready to rush into danger and save the day…watch out baddies, here comes the mighty Gekko!
 
Newton Star - Newton is an ordinary, book-obsessed kid by day from a different city to the PJ’s, but by night he transforms into protector of space – Newton Star! 
 
An Yu - Protector of Mystery Mountain, she’s an ancient soul, half-girl half-dragon, freed after being trapped inside the Dragin Gong for 1000 years.
 
Armadylan - A big, strong kid, who thinks he’s one of the heroes! Armadylan’s pyjamas turn into a bulky suit of armour, armadillo-style.
 
Romeo - A marvel of mechanical mischief, meet mad scientist Romeo. With all his amazing inventions he plans to take over the world!
 
Luna Girl - Luna Girl wants all the daytime things for herself – and she’ll have a terrible tantrum if she doesn’t get her way!
 
Night Ninja - A splat-sticking, back-flipping Ninja who wants to show everyone that he’s the best at everything!
 
PJ Robot - Friend of the PJ Masks, this miniature inventor is the keeper of HQ and unlocks the heroes’ new superpowers! 
 
 
TUNE IN to PJ Masks Official for your favourite full episodes of the PJ Masks Cartoon. Here you will see daily kids videos for kids and kids cartoons for your favourite superheroes for kids!
 
SUBSCRIBE for more Cartoons for Kids for the kids tv show PJ Masks & PJ Masks Power Heroes. Join Amaya, Connor and Greg as they transform into superheroes during the night and use their powers to fight villains and solve mysteries.

title: Booba - Climbing Challenge! - Cartoon for kids
description:
Get ready for a hilarious #climb! 🧗‍♂️😂 Watch #Booba take on ladders, ropes, shelves, and more 🪜🧃📦 — he’s always reaching higher, and the #fun goes up with him! 🚀🎉 *Subscribe and watch new episodes* ▶ https://youtube.com/@Booba?sub_confirmation=1
Booba plush toy 👉 https://boobatv.com/boobashop
 
🛒 Welcome to the Booba merchandise store! ► https://boobatv.com/boobashop
 
ℹ️ It’s good to know that the original name of that small brownie is pronounced by small kids as #booba, #boba, #буба, #bobby, #bobba, #bupa, #боба, #buba, #баба, #bobaa, #بوبا, #bubba, #baba, #duba, #boombah and even #ﺏﻮﺑﺍ.
 
*Who is Booba?*
Booba is cute and inquisitive, like a five-year-old kid. He explores the world without anger or resentment, only with joy and wonder. He doesn't talk, although he does make sounds to express his emotions.
 
Nobody knows where he came from, but he has obviously missed the last 100 years of human progress and explores modern locations with boundless energy and enthusiasm. His awkward movements, combined with a strong desire to learn more about the world around him, often have hilarious results! However, this doesn’t satisfy Booba’s curiosity, so his adventures will continue in the upcoming series.

description:

In a vast natural reserve lost in the middle of the untamed wilderness, there is a small haven of human civilization: the forest ranger's house. Because he is (from his point of view) the most evolved animal on earth, the bear Grizzy feels it's only natural that the ranger's house becomes his territory as soon as its owner is away. No other animal dares to contest this "bear's privilege" except the most inoffensive, stupid and ridiculous mammal family that exists: the Lemmings - who also move into the house as soon as the ranger is gone. Grizzy and the Lemmings lead a merciless battle over the house in an atmosphere of total madness, where the two adversaries constantly try to outdo each other with nasty tricks!

Booba is cute and inquisitive, like a five-year-old kid. He explores the world without anger or resentment, only with joy and wonder. He doesn't talk, although he does make sounds to express his emotions.
 
Nobody knows where he came from, but he has obviously missed the last 100 years of human progress and explores modern locations with boundless energy and enthusiasm. title: Double Trouble | Grizzy & the lemmings | 30' Compilation | 🐻🐹 Cartoon for Kids
description:
👉 Subscribe for more videos: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCn9l4gU5mkmmlC2eiVu0LHw?sub_confirmation=1
 
In a vast natural reserve lost in the middle of the untamed wilderness, there is a small haven of human civilization: the forest ranger's house. Because he is (from his point of view) the most evolved animal on earth, the bear Grizzy feels it's only natural that the ranger's house becomes his territory as soon as its owner is away. No other animal dares to contest this "bear's privilege" except the most inoffensive, stupid and ridiculous mammal family that exists: the Lemmings - who also move into the house as soon as the ranger is gone. Grizzy and the Lemmings lead a merciless battle over the house in an atmosphere of total madness, where the two adversaries constantly try to outdo each other with nasty tricks!
 
In this compilation:
00:00:00 | Double Trouble | S04E64
00:06:29 | Badly Sprained Bear | S04E28

❤ Sheriff Labrador's Safety Talk ❤
Kids, when there's a flood, stay in a safe place. Don't run around!
Never walk through floodwater. The water can move really fast, and there might be whirlpools under that you can't see. You might get swept away!
Also, watch out for wires. They can shock you.
And wet food from a flood might be dirty. It can make you sick! So you shouldn't eat it!
Please remember that!

Get ready for a fun and emotional journey with Urulaikilangu Chellakutty on his special day! 🥳 It’s his birthday, but things don’t go as smoothly as planned. Here’s what happens:

🎂 Scene 1: Chellakutty goes to the cake shop to buy a birthday cake, but when the shopkeeper asks for money, he bursts into tears! 😢 Luckily, Mom comes to the rescue and consoles him with a big smile.

🎈 Scene 2: He tries to decorate the house but gets upset when the balloons pop! 🎈😭 Again, Mom comes to cheer him up with some magic balloons!

🎁 Scene 3: His friends apply cakes on his face as part of the celebration, but he gets frustrated and cries. Mom consoles him and makes him laugh! 🎁🎉

Finally, it’s time for the grand birthday party with friends, cake, and lots of fun! 🎊 Watch how Urulaikilangu Chellakutty goes from tears to giggles, teaching kids the importance of patience, family love, and celebrating together.

title: #KalariKids #funnyvideos #Kids #Comedy #Cartoons #shorts #adventure #KalariKidsShorts
description:
Kalari Kids is a popular 2D animated series created by Green Gold Animation. The show is set in the village of Kalaripuram, which preserves and practices the ancient martial art of Kalaripayattu. The kids from both Gurukuls are trained by two Gurus, who are two brothers with distinct ideologies. While Guru Palan believes in bringing out the best in his students with lighthearted methods and values their age and innocence, Guru Veta believes in a rigid, military form of training. Kalari Kids is an intellectual property of Green Gold Animation and is set in a fictional city known as Kalaripuram. This entertaining cartoon is aimed at young children who are interested in learning about ancient martial arts.

This show is popular among children due to its unique storylines and endless entertainment. It follows the adventures of the Kalari kids as they learn ancient art from Guru Palan and Guru Veta. This Hindi-Animated Stories show is the best cartoon with excellent animation in Hindi. It's perfect for kids and is packed with surprising plots and the best Hindi stories. Guru Palan’s Kalari kids team includes Beenu, Meena, Shyam, Unni, and Ami, and Guru Veta’s Kalari kids team includes Raaka, Dhana, Mani, Langot, and Lekha, who always strive to win against other teams. This Hindi cartoon story shows unity and innocence and glorifies the country's heritage and culture.

A light bulb flickers then comes on full! A car won’t start, but then just revs to life! A broken doorbell suddenly starts ringing again. How does that happen? Fixies, those tiny human like creatures that secretly keep all of our appliances and gadgets running smoothly!

Want to know more about Strawberry Shortcake and her friends?

Strawberry Shortcake is a chef and owner of Berry Bitty Café. She has magenta-red hair with a strawberry hat with a pink flower clip underneath, bright green eyes, wears a white T-shirt over a pink polka dot dress with lime green and white striped leggings and red mary janes. Her icon is a strawberry. She is confident, considerate, optimistic, thoughtful, resourceful, enthusiastic and full of ideas. Her pets are Custard the kitten and Pupcake the puppy.

Orange Blossom is a store manager and owner of Orange Mart. She has black-brown hair, brown-orange eyes, wears an orange dress with light orange and white striped leggings, an orange boots, and a camille flower clip with an orange in the center on her hair. Her icon is an orange. She is clever, energetic, ingenious, sporty, adventurous, caring and always ready to lend a hand. Her pet is Marmalade the puppy.

Lemon Meringue is a hairstylist and owner of the Lemon Beauty Salon. She has light yellow hair, sky-blue eyes, wears a yellow sweater, a light blue skirt with light yellow and white striped leggings, yellow mary janes, and a lemon clip on her hair. Her icon is a lemon. She is creative, stylish, girly and a quick-thinker who can fix any hair problem, such as a bad hair day. Her pet is Henna the puppy.

Blueberry Muffin is a bookworm and owner of Blueberry Bookstore. She has navy-blue hair, azure blue eyes, wears a blue cardigan over a light blue shirt with deep blue dots, a blue skirt with emerald-green and white striped leggings, blue flats, and a blue headband with a blueberry on it on her hair. Her icon is a blueberry. She is smart, intelligent, diligent and is quick to think about a problem first. Her pet is Scouty the puppy.

Raspberry Torte is a fashion designer and owner of Raspberry Boutique. She has magenta-pink hair, lavender-pink eyes, wears a short purple jacket over a deep pink dress with a light green long sleeves with light pink and white striped leggings, dark pink mary janes with a light pink strap, a raspberry bracelet, and a headband with a raspberry on it on her hair. Her icon is a raspberry. She is fashionable, friendly, polite and cares a lot about her fashions as much as her friends. Her pet is Chiffon the puppy.

Plum Pudding is a dancer and owner of Plum Dance Studio. She has purple-violet hair in a ponytail worn with a plum clip, deep purple eyes, wears a violet cardigan over a light purple and light blue dance dress, green and white striped leggings (in the TV show, one of her striped patterns is lavender), and purple ballet slippers with a violet legwarmers. title: Good Mother VS Bad Mother 🍐 Overprotective VS Too Busy 🍐 Pear Couple
description:
In this hilarious animation, we explore two very different kinds of moms and the family struggles they bring! Liza is the overprotective mom who’s all about healthy habits. 🥦📚 She makes her daughter Ashley wear a hat everywhere, eat veggies, and read books all day. Ashley, of course, thinks her mom is way too strict and doesn’t let her have any fun. 🙄

On the flip side, Carrot is the too busy mom. She spends most of her time working and showers her daughter Mira with toys and gadgets 🛍️📱, but rarely spends quality time with her. Mira gets everything she wants—except her mom’s attention, and she’s not happy about it.

This comedy showcases classic kids vs parents moments and funny hacks for parents as Ashley and Mira hilariously deal with their bad mom and good mom situations. A fun reminder that no mom is perfect, but love can fix anything! ❤️ Subscribe to our channel 🚨 https://www.youtube.com/@PearCouple
Don't forget to give a thumbs up if you want to see more videos soon!​ 👍

In the premiere episode of the animated series "Beadies," young viewers are introduced to Cheep and his mother, Coco the Hen, who live on the enchanting yellow page of the magical album. Together with these endearing characters, children embark on a delightful journey, learning the art of greetings and the construction of pyramids. As the episode draws to a close, they are serenaded with enchanting music, preparing them for the sweetest of dreams.

Beadies is a developmental musical cartoon series for kids up to four years of age. Created by a team of animators, child psychologists, teachers and parents. Beadies uses play to provide comprehensive child development while accounting for a child’s perception. Most importantly, we put our hearts into making Beadies.

title: Chase and Rescue Mission | PJ Masks Official | Cartoons for Kids | Animation for Kids | FULL Episode
description:
Brand NEW Episodes only on Disney Junior
►Subscribe for more PJ Masks videos: http://bit.ly/2gsj5gv
 
PJ Masks Power Heroes - Power heroes Catboy, Owlette and Gekko are joined by new heroes, creating a bigger, even better team. Good thing, too, as new villains are in town. Our heroes will take them on in the city, space, and the frozen wilderness of Iceworld. As Catboy says, “if badness is everywhere, we’ll be everywhere.” 
 
PJ Masks - By day 6 year olds Connor, Amaya and Greg go to school like everyone else. But when something goes awry in the city, these special kids, filled with curiosity and a sense of justice get ready for their mission – but they have to wait until night fall when the city is asleep and they can go un detected. Instead of going to bed like all the other children, when our heroes get their pyjamas on, they magically transform into super heroes and become the PJ Masks. Here come Catboy – super fast and agile, Gekko – super strong and can scale walls and Owlette – with the ability to fly and see great distances. Together these three can tackle any situation – PJ Masks they’re on their way into the night to save the day!
 
Meet The Characters: 
 
Catboy - Incredibly fast! Amazingly agile! Able to hear the quietest sounds across unbelievable distances. When adventure beckons, the amazing Catboy leaps to the rescue!
 
Owlette - She can fly! Has super eyesight! And when she flaps her powerful wings, the baddies are sent flying… Keep your “Owl Eyes!” on Owlette!
 
Gekko - He’s strong, sticky and a master of camouflage! He’s ready to rush into danger and save the day…watch out baddies, here comes the mighty Gekko!
 
Newton Star - Newton is an ordinary, book-obsessed kid by day from a different city to the PJ’s, but by night he transforms into protector of space – Newton Star! 
 
An Yu - Protector of Mystery Mountain, she’s an ancient soul, half-girl half-dragon, freed after being trapped inside the Dragin Gong for 1000 years.
 
Armadylan - A big, strong kid, who thinks he’s one of the heroes! Armadylan’s pyjamas turn into a bulky suit of armour, armadillo-style.
 
Romeo - A marvel of mechanical mischief, meet mad scientist Romeo. With all his amazing inventions he plans to take over the world!
 
Luna Girl - Luna Girl wants all the daytime things for herself – and she’ll have a terrible tantrum if she doesn’t get her way!
 
Night Ninja - A splat-sticking, back-flipping Ninja who wants to show everyone that he’s the best at everything!
 
PJ Robot - Friend of the PJ Masks, this miniature inventor is the keeper of HQ and unlocks the heroes’ new superpowers! 
 
 
TUNE IN to PJ Masks Official for your favourite full episodes of the PJ Masks Cartoon. Here you will see daily kids videos for kids and kids cartoons for your favourite superheroes for kids!
 
SUBSCRIBE for more Cartoons for Kids for the kids tv show PJ Masks & PJ Masks Power Heroes. Join Amaya, Connor and Greg as they transform into superheroes during the night and use their powers to fight villains and solve mysteries.

❤ Sheriff Labrador's Safety Talk ❤
Kids, even though smells can’t be seen or touched, they can help the police solve cases!
If someone leaves behind a smell—like from a lost item, a missing person, or a runaway baddie—police can follow that smell to find them.
Even if the baddie tries to hide the smell, the police can still find them!
Isn’t it amazing?

மனசெல்லோம் ச ண் ளமயோகும்.

Friendship ★ A friend in need, a friend indeed!
Adorable as ever, Kathu is a true friend in need. The daring and spirited Kathu doesn’t hesitate any, going all the way to save her friend Appu. Watch this story that demonstrates the definition of friendship and the power of love. Some surprises in store too. Turns out, bad guys are not bad after all!

Theme song ★ Let’s go playing, Kathu !
Celebrate Kathu, the darling of family and friends with this fun song. Staying true to the natural landscape and life, this song is a good reference for youngsters on the local sights and sounds. Nostalgia for the elders and great wonderment for children!

Planning ★ Kathu saves Mittu 
Kathu and her friend Appu successfully escaped the fierce clutches of the eagle but now they are lost in a jungle and can’t remember their way back home.  Luckily, they find a new friend who invites them for a tour of the jungle. The wilderness is as beautiful as it’s dangerous. Discover how cleverly Kathu saves herself and her friends.

Leadership ★ Kathu, the brave
A continuation of the jungle adventures! Mittu reunites with Kathu & Appu. Where? How about a jungle café? Oh boy! There is a menu for almost everyone. Vegetarians, this way! So, will Kathu and Appu finally get to take a break from adventures and get some rest? Or is it ‘always- on-your- toes’ in the jungle?

Generosity ★ Kathu, the generous
In the jungle, there are few friends and more enemies. So, keep your ears pricked!  And what happens in the mainland, happens in the wilderness too, with an extra touch of hazard.  Will a predator in the city become prey in the jungle?  Follow Kathu and Appu as they continue to encounter more danger! 

Hope ★ Kathu and the big cat
It is nice to know that finally Kathu and Appu would be going home. Are they? What will stop them from returning to their village? Suspense and excitement as the story unfold! Is a visit to the jungle complete without a glimpse of the big guys?  Why wait to find out! Tick-tock, tick-tock, the clock’s ticking!

Kathu Volume 4 ★ The Jungle Safari
It's Kathu's day out! We have seen her in the adventures in and around home ground.
In Volume 4, it's Kathu and Appu's journey from the familiar to the unfamiliar, from the country to the forest. Things are always taking a turn towards more and more adventures!
Do not miss the jungle gang! They are fearsome and mean! Kathu has her hands full.
Time to find out how Kathu & her companion Appu tackles them.

Spookiz 스푸키즈 follows the lives of Cula, Frankie and all their friends whilst at school. 

Cula is a descendant of a royal Dracula family. He may seem cold-blooded and evil, but he actually wants to get close to others and become their friends. He has OCD and a complete neat freak! You may see him and his sidekick KongKong get up to no good, but he's a good soul really!

Frankie is a bit of a dull slowpoke, Frankie's appetite sometimes turns him into a bit of a monster! He grows a four-leaf clover on top of his head which is lucky charm. He's one of the kindest members of the Spookiz gang, but his appetite sometimes puts him in a foul mood if he is not full up!

Kebi is a free-minded soul and isn't one to stick to rules and formality. He's constantly energetic and bubbly and loves to tease Cula as much as he can. It is a friendly rivalry though as they truly are best buddies!

KongKong is Cula's sidekick KongKong is best described as weak to the strong and strong to the weak. He's very self conscious about his short height but by listening and trusting in Cula he feels safe and comforted.

Zizi shows gives off a stinking odour but she does not realise it. Body parts (mainly her head) often fall apart off her body, but are always easily placed back together on her. She has a secret crush on Cula and dreams of being with him always. She's incredibly shy around him and doesn't like anyone to know this.

Mila and Morphle work together to help others and protect their City from the misbehaving Bandits and mischievous Orphle. Through courage, imagination and most of all, teamwork, they are able to solve any problem and save the day.

Booba is cute and inquisitive, like a five-year-old kid. He explores the world without anger or resentment, only with joy and wonder. He doesn't talk, although he does make sounds to express his emotions.

About Peppa Pig official channel:

Welcome to the Official Peppa Pig channel and the home of Peppa on YouTube!  We have created a world of Peppa with episodes and compilations to keep even the most dedicated Peppa fans happy.  Here at Peppa Pig Official channel, kids can be happy and smart! Watch Peppa Pig clips and episodes where Peppa Pig play games with her friends, Mummy Pig and Daddy Pig tell the bedtime stories, Peppa Pig sings nursery rhymes and songs, Peppa and her family and friends celebrate Christmas and Halloween together! Peppa Pig episodic animation, Peppa Pig songs for kids, Peppa Pig toy play and Peppa Pig Stop motion create a world that centres on the everyday experiences of young children.  Enjoy and don't forget to subscribe.

Peppa is a loveable, cheeky little piggy who lives with her little brother George, Mummy Pig and Daddy Pig. Peppa’s favourite things include playing games and music, learning animal sounds, dressing up, days out,  shopping, holidays and jumping in muddy puddles. Her adventures always end happily with loud snorts of laughter.

Meet Peppa Pig and her family:

Peppa Pig
Peppa Pig is a lovable but slightly bossy little pig. She is four years old and lives with Mummy Pig, Daddy Pig and her little brother George. Peppa likes playing with her best friend Suzy Sheep, visiting Granny and Grandpa Pig and looking after George. Most of all, Peppa loves jumping up and down in muddy puddles, laughing and making loud snorting noises.

George Pig
George is Peppa’s little brother. He is 18 months old and loves to play with his big sister, Peppa – even when she’s being bossy. George’s favourite thing is his toy dinosaur. He carries it everywhere with him. George can’t speak yet but can say one word very well: ‘Dine-saw!’

Mummy Pig
Mummy Pig likes jumping up and down in muddy puddles almost as much as Peppa. She works from home on her computer and sometimes lets Peppa and George help, as long as they don’t bash the keyboard. She is better at map reading than Daddy Pig and is very wise about most things.

Daddy Pig
Daddy Pig is very jolly and laughs all the time, especially when he plays with Peppa and George. Daddy Pig reads the paper and gets excited about trips in the car. He loves cookies and pumpkin pie and Peppa teases him about his big round tummy. Daddy Pig can be a tiny bit grumpy sometimes when he can’t remember where he put his glasses.

Have fun with Peppa Pig and her friends: Suzy Sheep,Rebecca Rabbit,Danny Dog,Candy Cat,Pedro Pony,Zoe Zebra,Emily Elephant,Freddy Fox,Kylie Kangaroo,Wendy Wolf,Gabriella Goat,Gerald Giraffe,Molly Mole,Belinda Bear,Delphine Donkey, Peggi and Pandora Panda,Mandy Mouse,Simon Squirrel!

Meet Peppa Pig's family:

Peppa Pig
Peppa Pig is a lovable but slightly bossy little pig. She is four years old and lives with Mummy Pig, Daddy Pig and her little brother George. Peppa likes playing with her best friend Suzy Sheep, visiting Granny and Grandpa Pig and looking after George. Most of all, Peppa loves jumping up and down in muddy puddles, laughing and making loud snorting noises.

George Pig
George is Peppa’s little brother. He is 18 months old and loves to play with his big sister, Peppa – even when she’s being bossy. George’s favourite thing is his toy dinosaur. He carries it everywhere with him. George can’t speak yet but can say one word very well: ‘Dine-saw!’

Mummy Pig
Mummy Pig likes jumping up and down in muddy puddles almost as much as Peppa. She works from home on her computer and sometimes lets Peppa and George help, as long as they don’t bash the keyboard. She is better at map reading than Daddy Pig and is very wise about most things.

Daddy Pig
Daddy Pig is very jolly and laughs all the time, especially when he plays with Peppa and George. Daddy Pig reads the paper and gets excited about trips in the car. He loves cookies and pumpkin pie and Peppa teases him about his big round tummy. Daddy Pig can be a tiny bit grumpy sometimes when he can’t remember where he put his glasses.

Have fun with Peppa Pig and her friends: Suzy Sheep, Rebecca Rabbit, Danny Dog, Candy Cat, Pedro Pony, Zoe Zebra, Emily Elephant, Freddy Fox, Kylie Kangaroo, Wendy Wolf, Gabriella Goat, Gerald Giraffe, Molly Mole, Belinda Bear, Delphine Donkey, Peggi and Pandora Panda, Mandy Mouse, Simon Squirrel!

Welcome to the official Shaun the Sheep YouTube channel - home to Shaun, Timmy, the Flock, Bitzer, the Farmer and their friends! 🐑🐕👨‍🌾

Shaun is a sheep who doesn't follow the flock - in fact, he leads them into all sorts of scrapes and scraps, turning peace in the valley into mayhem in the meadow. Shaun and his pals run rings around their poor sheepdog Bitzer, as he tries to stop the Farmer finding out what's going on behind his back. Every day brings a new adventure for Shaun! The company has an extensive collection of classic animated shows that are loved by kids worldwide, such as Chhota Bheem, Super Bheem, Mighty Little Bheem, Krishna Balram, and Mighty Raju, among others. 

In 2011, Green Gold Animation launched Green Gold TV, an official YouTube channel exclusively created for children, providing them with a dedicated space to watch their favourite animated shows. The channel features a diverse selection of episodes, ensuring an enjoyable viewing experience for children. Some of the notable shows featured on the channel include Chhota Bheem, Super Bheem, Mighty Little Bheem, Kalari Kids, Krishna Balram, Mighty Raju, and many more. Children can easily watch their favourite shows on Green Gold TV at any time and from any place. The channel is replete with exciting and engaging content guaranteed to captivate and entertain children for extended periods. Whether it's Chhota Bheem or any other offering, Green Gold TV stands as the ultimate destination for children seeking enjoyable and entertaining shows.

Green Gold TV is a channel designed specifically for children, providing them with a wide range of both entertaining and educational content. The channel presents animated videos that are not only enjoyable but also informative, showcasing popular shows from Cartoon Network, Hindi moral stories, engaging animations, and overall entertaining content for children. One particular highlight is the inclusion of the beloved Chhota Bheem series, featuring beloved characters such as Bheem, Jaggu, Kalia, Chutki, Raju, Dholu, and Bholu. Our shows are also available on various OTT platforms. The channel invites viewers to join for bedtime stories, offering hours of fun and learning.

Booba is cute and inquisitive, like a five-year-old kid. He explores the world without anger or resentment, only with joy and wonder. He doesn't talk, although he does make sounds to express his emotions.

title: Krishna Animated Movie With English Subtitles | HD 1080p | Animated Movies For Kids In Hindi
description:
One of the most recognizable, loved figures of Indian culture and mythology, Krishna and his stories make for an arresting, riveting tale. The extra-ordinary tale of Lord Krishna's birth, his adventures as a kid, his pranks and playfulness, his bonding with everyone who comes across him and the devotion he evokes, is captured and brought to light in this wholesome, enchanting animation film.
 This film narrates the tale from Krishna's childhood friend, Sudama's perspective. It traces the life of Krishna from his birth in the prison cell of Kansa, to his growing years in Vrindavan and Gokul, to his victory over his evil uncle Kansa, finally how as the king of Dwarka, Krishna, the all knowing, embraces everyone from all walks of life, including his childhood friend Sudama, as an equal. 👉 Log On To Our Official Website : https://penstudios.in/
